TITLE Resolution Function of Studsvik obtained from  Si3N4 (lambda=1.47240 angstroms)
! To be used with IRESO=1 in FullProf.2k (version > 1.6)
JOBT CW Neutrons
!     Lambda1    Lambda2   Ratio(I2/I1)
WAVE  1.47240    1.47240      0.0
!    NPROF    Shape1    Shape2   Shape3
PROF    7        0.0       0.0      0.0
!  Cos(2thM)^2 for polarization = 0 for neutrons
CTHM  0.0
!     2theta-min   step   2theta-max
THRG     2.0       0.05      140.00
!   Uins         Vins         Wins       Xins      Yins      Zins
UVWXYZ  1.359297    -0.647594     0.176295   0.00000   0.00000     0.000
